{"tid":1520561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[獅子座] 真係好難忘記一個人","createTime":"2019-08-31T00:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:24:11.000Z","uid":69020,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"095e3a7abd4436e037f96a7ee6f6edf56f93c4b6","tid":1520561,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"我好難鍾意人<br />\n<br />\n我係獅女，佢係蟹仔，佢係我初戀亦係第一個鍾意嘅人，三年前識佢好快就鍾意咗佢，我明知我地性格、興趣同生活習慣都好唔夾，依然想試一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年後我地一齊咗，一齊之後佢好錫我，但可能真係太唔夾，我又唔想成日嘈交，所以盡量遷就、理解佢，但久而久之令到我拍拖拍得好辛苦，七個月後我提出咗分手<br />\n<br />\n佢有挽留，我亦都仲鍾意佢，但心裡明白就算再一齊落去都唔會開心，成日遷就退讓根本就唔係我性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分手後我好快就move on咗，但我到宜家深夜都會間中諗起佢(純粹諗起佢，已經冇傷心嘅感覺)，佢po story我會即睇，佢搵我我會秒覆，雖然我同佢冇可能，但好難將佢完全在心中抹去，至少係下一個我鍾意嘅人出現之前"},{"pid":"ea9ce6bdc4134788533a956976714261ff0f931d","tid":1520561,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T00:43:23.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2Wo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=3ccb9d32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"ht